Invoice <%= @invoice.invoice_number %>

Hi <%= @account.name %>,
Thanks for using VersionLab. Here is the breakdown of your latest charge.

<% @line_items.each do |li| -%>
  <%= li.description %> (qty <%= li.quantity %>) — $<%= format('%.2f', li.amount_cents / 100.0) %>
